<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“我与国旗同框，青春献礼祖国”</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">镜头捕捉刹那，铭刻时代风华</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">以镜头传递赤诚</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">每一帧影像，皆是忠的咏叹</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">每一份热忱，皆在镜头下熠熠闪光</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;经管学子以韶华之姿，致敬祖国</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250507 甘梓涵</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936369521.jpg" alt="1760936369521.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936369521.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936384876.jpg" alt="1760936384876.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936384876.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250505 帅思琪</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936429312.jpg" alt="1760936429312.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936429312.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B240509 叶星</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936476067.png" alt="1760936476067.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936476067.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B240501 邹紫洁</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936507799.jpg" alt="1760936507799.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936507799.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>C240516 许硕肖</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936548879.jpg" alt="1760936548879.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936548879.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>.B250513 凌欢</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936596784.jpg" alt="1760936596784.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936596784.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B240506 钟升阳</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936630223.jpg" alt="1760936630223.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936630223.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B240501 赵可欣</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936671007.jpg" alt="1760936671007.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936671007.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250505 邓忆珊</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936707199.jpg" alt="1760936707199.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936707199.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Z250515 祝赞磊</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936752257.jpg" alt="1760936752257.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936752257.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250507 郑代权</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936790208.jpg" alt="1760936790208.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936790208.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250512 张凡</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936812806.jpg" alt="1760936812806.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936812806.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250505 郭诗梵</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936858840.jpg" alt="1760936858840.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936858840.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250507 杨雨涵</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936904284.jpg" alt="1760936904284.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936904284.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250507 曾润珠</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936949649.jpg" alt="1760936949649.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936949649.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250505 李林华</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936983235.jpg" alt="1760936983235.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760936983235.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B240501 郭红艳</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937007233.jpg" alt="1760937007233.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937007233.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250506 胡骁</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937026734.jpg" alt="1760937026734.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937026734.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>B250511 董钰玲</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937051763.jpg" alt="1760937051763.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1760937051763.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">我们沐浴在新时代的阳光下</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">仰望着那一抹中国红</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">漫漫征途上</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这是指引我们前行的光</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此刻 &nbsp;让我们大声告白</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 我爱你，中国！</span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p><br></p>